### Generate a small snippet
POST http://localhost:8000/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prompt": "create a python function to compute fibonacci with memoization",
  "project_name": "fib_demo"
}

### Generate a full project (async)
POST http://localhost:8000/generate/project
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prompt": "Create a FastAPI Todo app with SQLite and JWT auth, plus tests and Docker.",
  "project_name": "todo_app",
  "auto_test": true,
  "config": {
    "coder_model": "deepseek-coder:6.7b",
    "refiner_model": "qwen2.5:7b",
    "fix_model": "codellama:13b",
    "temperature": 0.2
  }
}

### Stream refined prompt
POST http://localhost:8000/generate/stream
Content-Type: application/json

{ "prompt": "build me a CLI password manager in Go" }

### Run tests on a generated project
POST http://localhost:8000/test
Content-Type: application/json

{ "project_path": "./generated_projects/todo_app" }

### Ask the fixer to repair a project given an error log
POST http://localhost:8000/fix
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "project_path": "./generated_projects/todo_app",
  "error_log": "ModuleNotFoundError: No module named 'app.models'"
}

### Job status
GET http://localhost:8000/status

### Single job
GET http://localhost:8000/status/JOB_ID_HERE

### Logs
GET http://localhost:8000/logs/JOB_ID_HERE

### Plans
GET http://localhost:8000/plans

### Read a specific plan
GET http://localhost:8000/plans/todo_app
